parent.sql: SELECT "Contests".*, "Offers"."id" AS "Offers.id" FROM (SELECT "Contests"."id", "Contests"."orderId", "Contests"."userId", "Contests"."contestType", "Contests"."fileName", "Contests"."originalFileName", "Contests"."title", "Contests"."typeOfName", "Contests"."industry", "Contests"."focusOfWork", "Contests"."targetCustomer", "Contests"."styleName", "Contests"."nameVenture", "Contests"."typeOfTagline", "Contests"."brandStyle", "Contests"."createdAt", "Contests"."status", "Contests"."prize", "Contests"."priority", "Contests"."isVerified" FROM "Contests" AS "Contests" WHERE "Contests"."status" = 'active' AND "Contests"."userId" = 1 ORDER BY "Contests"."id" DESC LIMIT 8 OFFSET 0) AS "Contests" LEFT OUTER JOIN "Offers" AS "Offers" ON "Contests"."id" = "Offers"."contestId" ORDER BY "Contests"."id" DESC;
